answersResultList.title: You're getting over your ex.
answersResultList.resultContent: Those pangs of doubt and regret get a little fainter every day, along with that nasty urge for revenge dating. You're entertaining wholesome fantasies about someone else, but it feels too soon. Staying away from your ex's family or friends doesn't hurt as much as before. You'll beat this thing and come out of it a better person.
